snippet.title: Leaked Audio EXPOSES Amber Heard's Lies About Ex-Husband Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Hiiiiiii chismosas ☎️

In today’s video, I talk about The Daily Mail releasing audio from Amber Heard and Johnny Depp’s 2015 therapy sessions where Amber reveals that she was abusive toward her husband and started multiple physical altercations.

LET ME KNOW DOWN BELOW IN THE COMMENTS  → Do you think she should be fired from her current projects now that these truths about her former marriage have been revealed?
